Commands: 

new r t w h
creates a new maze
r - road length (default 3)
t - road thickness (default 1)
w - maze width (default 48)
h - maze height (default 48)

style n
changes style

color/colorbg n
changes foreground/background color

font n
changes font

fontb
previous font

pause
pauses the game

replay n
adjusts replay speed

t
toggle tile numbers

p
toggle path/wall numbers

Hints & Tips: 
Try using the commands without 
parameters!
Try style 3!
Try dimensions that are multiples
of your road length!
Hit enter to repeat the last
command!